: male, Myanmar (Burma), 50 km E Putao, env. Nan Thi village, 950 m, 11-16. V.1998, leg. Murzin &amp; Sinjaev, slide ZSM Arct. 2019-806 Volynkin (MWM/ ZSM). 
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="167">Paratypes</emphasis>
